### 1. Login User
POST http://localhost:4015/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@mail.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 2. Create Payment (Role USER or ADMIN. Ganti orderId dengan order ID milik user ini)
POST http://localhost:4015/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "transactionId": "TX-MANUAL-12345",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "paymentMethod": "TRANSFER",
  "paymentProof": "https://example.com/payment-proof.png",
  "metadata": {
    "bank": "BCA",
    "senderName": "John Doe"
  }
}

### 3. Get All Payments (USER gets self, ADMIN gets all)
GET http://localhost:4015/api/payments

### 4. Get Payment by ID
GET http://localhost:4015/api/payments/1

### 5. Login Admin
POST http://localhost:4015/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mail.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 6. Update Payment (Only ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:4015/api/payments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SETTLEMENT",
  "metadata": {
    "bank": "BCA",
    "senderName": "John Doe",
    "verifiedBy": "Admin Alice"
  }
}

### 7. Delete Payment (Only ADMIN)
DELETE http://localhost:4015/api/payments/1
